{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8b889a50f6","title":"中共中央关于成立中央组织宣传组的决定","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"22a55d3273","index":0,"year":1970,"month":11,"day":6,"articleId":"8b889a50f6","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"重要党政机构及其衍变","id":"318138ea26","type":"主题"},{"name":"张春桥","id":"471a503675","type":"人物"},{"name":"康生","id":"57eea82497","type":"人物"},{"name":"江青","id":"82305e518c","type":"人物"},{"name":"姚文元","id":"92a8a42842","type":"人物"},{"name":"中共中央决定、指示等","id":"94b82e4994","type":"发行机构"},{"name":"纪登奎","id":"9a50528209","type":"人物"},{"name":"指导理论","id":"c1c0033e04","type":"主题"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"中央文件","id":"ef6e778547","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"李德生","id":"f3ee2f4a99","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"868a7c5d7f","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于成立中央组织宣传组的决定","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8b889a50f6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e6633c20fb","type":"paragraph","text":"一、为了党在目前进行的组织宣传工作，实施统一管理，中央决定在中央政治局领导下，设立中央组织宣传组。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8b889a50f6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"81a694f1bf","type":"paragraph","text":"二、中央组织宣传组设组长一人，由康生同志担任，设组员若干人，由江青、张春桥、姚文元、纪登奎、李德生同志担任。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8b889a50f6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"070d400fac","type":"paragraph","text":"三、中央组织宣传组管辖中央组织部、中央党校、人民日报、红旗杂志、新华总社、中央广播事业局、光明日报、中央编译局的工作，以及中央划归该组管辖单位的工作。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8b889a50f6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e236a9a918","type":"paragraph","text":"四、工，青、妇中央一级机构和它们的五·七干校，均划归中央组织宣传组管辖。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8b889a50f6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"993e78132f","type":"paragraph","text":"五、中央组织宣传组可设短小精干的联络办公室。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8b889a50f6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"381f4070b2","type":"paragraph","text":"六、中央旧中宣部、政治研究室均取消，归中央办公厅负责管理它们的五·七干校和安置工作。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8b889a50f6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4fd41958dd","type":"paragraph","text":"（此件发至省、军级）","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8b889a50f6","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}